	              		<content>  
	                  		<Input id="email" type="Email" value=""/>
	                  		<Input id="password" type="Password" value=""/>
	                  		<Button text="Login" press="login"/>
	             		</content>
	             	</Panel>
        		</content>
   			</Page> -->
			<Page title="OpenUI5 Stock Monitor App">
				<content>
					<IconTabBar>
						<items>
							<IconTabFilter text="Alerts">
								<Panel headerText="Price Alerts">
									<Panel headerText="Your Price Alerts">
										<List items="{alertList>/alerts}" mode="Delete" delete="deleteAlert" noDataText="No alerts set yet...">
											<StandardListItem title="{parts:[{path: 'alertList>stock'},{path: 'alertList>option'}, {path: 'alertList>price'}], formatter:'formatTitle'}" info="{alertList>note}"/>
										</List>
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Set Price Alert">
										<content>
											<layout:Grid>
											<Text text="Set an email alert when:" class="sapUiSmallMargin">
												<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L4 M3 S12"/>
												</layoutData>
											</Text>
											<Input value="{alertInput>/stock}" placeholder="Stock ticker..." liveChange="liveInputChange" valueLiveUpdate="true" type="Text" id="stockInput">
												<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L3 M3 S12"/>
												</layoutData>
											</Input>
											<ComboBox value="{alertInput>/option}" placeholder="Choose option..." type="Text" id="optionInput">
												<core:ListItem key="above" text="rises above"/>
												<core:ListItem key="below" text="falls below"/>
												<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L2 M3 S12"/>
												</layoutData>
											</ComboBox>
											<Text text="$" class="sapUiSmallMargin">
												<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L1 M3 S6"/>
												</layoutData>
											</Text>
											<Input value="{alertInput>/price}" placeholder="Price..." valueLiveUpdate="true" type="Number" id="priceInput">
												<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L1 M3 S6"/>
												</layoutData>
											</Input>
											<Input value="{alertInput>/note}" placeholder="Custom note here..." valueLiveUpdate="true" type="Text" id="noteInput">
												<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L8 M3 S6"/>
												</layoutData>
											</Input>
											<Button icon="sap-icon://save" press="submit">
											<layoutData>
													<layout:GridData span="L4 M3 S12"/>
												</layoutData>
											</Button>
											</layout:Grid>
										</content>
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
								<Panel headerText="Watch List">
									<Panel headerText="Your Watch List">

									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Add To Watch List">

									</Panel>
								</Panel>
							</IconTabFilter>
							<IconTabFilter text="Rule #1 Analysis">
								<Input value="{currentStock}" placeholder="Company's stock ticker here. The rest is automatic... :D "/>
								<Panel headerText="1. Meaning">
									<Panel headerText="Company Description">
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Company Industry Sector">
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
								<Panel headerText="2. Moat">
									<Panel headerText="The Big Five">
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
								
								<Panel headerText="3. Managament">
									<Panel headerText="CEO">
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Insider Trading">
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
								<Panel headerText="4. Margin of Safety">
									<Panel headerText="Sticker Price">
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="MOS Price">
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Current Price">
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
								<Panel text="Buy/Sell - The Three Tools">
									<Panel headerText="Moving Average Convergence Divergence">
										<ComboBox placeholder="Select Type of MACD..." type="Text">
											<core:ListItem key="12-26-9" text="12-26-9 (Standard)"/>
											<core:ListItem key="8-17-9" text="8-17-9 (Sensitive)"/>
											<layoutData>
												<layout:GridData span="L2 M3 S12"/>
											</layoutData>
										</ComboBox>
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Stochastic">
										<ComboBox placeholder="Select Type..." type="Text">
											<core:ListItem key="5-5" text="5-5 (Standard)"/>
											<core:ListItem key="14-5" text="14-5 (Sensitive)"/>
											<layoutData>
												<layout:GridData span="L2 M3 S12"/>
											</layoutData>
										</ComboBox>
									</Panel>
									<Panel headerText="Moving Average">
										<ComboBox placeholder="Select Type..." type="Text">
											<core:ListItem key="10Day" text="10 Day"/>
											<core:ListItem key="50Day" text="50 Day"/>
											<layoutData>
												<layout:GridData span="L2 M3 S12"/>
											</layoutData>
										</ComboBox>
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
								<Panel headerText="Overall Conclusion">
									<Panel>
										<Text text="BUY">
											<layoutData>
												<layout:GridData span="L6 M6 S6"/>
											</layoutData>
										</Text>
										<core:Icon src="sap-icon://thumb-up" color="green"/>
									</Panel>
									<Panel>
										<Text text="SELL">
											<layoutData>
												<layout:GridData span="L6 M6 S6"/>
											</layoutData>
										</Text>
										<core:Icon src="sap-icon://thumb-down" color="red"/>
										<Button icon="sap-icon//accept" text="Put on Watch List" press="addToWatchList"/>
									</Panel>
								</Panel>
							</IconTabFilter>
						</items>
					</IconTabBar>
					
				</content>
				<footer>
					<OverflowToolbar id="otbFooter">
						<ToolbarSpacer/>
						<Button text="Written by Christopher Frewin Â© 2017. Company and stock information are provided by finviz.com and the Yahoo! finance API." enabled="false"/>
						<Button icon="sap-icon://sap-ui5" text="App powered by SAPUI5" enabled="false"/>
					</OverflowToolbar>
				</footer>
			</Page>
		</pages>
	</App>
</mvc:View>